Class User

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
HDBApplicant, HDBManager
public abstract class User extends Object
Represents an abstract base class for all users in the system. Handles common attributes like NRIC, password, names, age, and marital status.
